name: shell pearl drop shaped earrings
description:
A contemporary and timeless pair of shell pearl drop earrings.

These classic earrings will look beautiful on anyone, whether you are working at an office, as a teacher in school, as an assistant in a shop or at a celebration of any kind. They also very easily take you from day to night.

The earrings are made from 12dt gold-plated sterling silver or sterling silver and drop shaped shell pearls in natural white.The earrings measure 3cm in length.

The earrings come wrapped in colourful tissue paper and slipped into an elegant white gift box, ready to be given as a gift to someone special or simply for you to keep.

name: Handmade Antique Rose Swarovski Crystal Drop Earrings
description:
This handmade and incredibly glamorous antique rose swarovski crystal drop earrings were made using the wire-wrap technique in my London studio.

These earrings will be a fabulous accessory for any festive occasions such as weddings, birthday parties or New Years eve. The unusual cut and colour of these swarovski crystals paired with the gorgeous large ear hooks make for a dramatic and festive look.

The earrings come in sterling silver or gold with matching petite bicone crystals and measure 5.5cm in length. 

The earrings come wrapped in colourful, crisp tissue paper and slipped into an elegant white gift box, ready to be given as a gift to someone special, or simply for you to keep.

name: Handmade Brushed Gold Drop Shaped Earrings
description:
This pair of brushed gold drop shaped earrings is very versatile and contemporary. They will go really well with structured outfits such as shift dresses as well as any outfits which include blazers.

The earrings are made of brushed 14ct gold-filled decorative parts and rings, 12ct gold plated sterling silver drop shaped wire parts as well as 12ct gold plated sterling silver hooks. Together the parts make an elegant pair of earrings which will take you from day to night when desired.

The earrings measure approximately 6 cm in length.

The earrings come wrapped in colourful paper and slipped into a beautiful white gift box, perfect for giving as a gift or simply for you to keep.

name: Swarovski Rondelle Crystal Earrings
description:
A glamourous and glittery pair of swarovski crystal earrings, handmade using the wire-wrap technique.

The earrings are very versatile; They will look great dressed down with s gorgeous jumper or shirt and smart trousers, or indeed, dressed to impress paired with your most elegant and dressy outfit.

The earrings are made of swarovski rondelles as well as swarovski rhinestone silver- or gold-plated rondelles paired with either sterling silver or 12ct gold-plated sterling silver.

They measure 3.5 cm in length.


The earrings are wrapped in colourful tissue paper and slipped into an elegant white gift box, ready to be given as a gift to someone special or simply for you to keep.

name: Faceted Amazonite and Circle Drop Earrings
description:
This stunning pair of earrings are exotic and glam and make me think of sunny, sandy beaches and crisp, chilled white wine. I think these will go exceptionally well with tanned skin and white summery clothes. Having said that, they will also look great with a floaty bohemian summer outfit.

As each piece is made by hand, they're all a little different, which makes them extra unique.

They consist of faceted amazonite gems, freshwater pearls and 12ct 
gold-plated sterling silver elements or sterling silver elements.

The earrings measure 3 cm in length. They come with rubber stoppers to slide onto the back of the earrings so you don't loose them.

The earrings come wrapped in colourful paper and slipped into an elegant white gift box, ready to give as a present or for you to keep.
